## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational and personal use only. Users are 
responsible for complying with the terms of service of any websites they 
scrape. The authors assume no responsibility for misuse of this software.

Web scraping should be done responsibly:
- Respect robots.txt files
- Implement rate limiting
- Don't overload servers
- Use official APIs when available
- Comply with website terms of service
- Don't scrape personal data without consent

By using this software, you agree to use it responsibly and ethically.
